#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starting a Game"
msgstr "Mängu alustamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:137
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you are familiar with the workings of the application, a game can be "
"started by pressing the <guibutton>Start</guibutton> button in the center of "
"the screen. This <quote>powers on</quote> the device, as shown by the "
"illuminated <interface>score counter</interface>. You can then "
"<action>choose the difficulty level</action> that you want to attempt:"
msgstr ""
"Kui oled rakendusega esmatutvuse sõlminud, saad alustada mängu, klõpsates "
"keset akent asuvale nupule <guibutton>Alusta</guibutton>. Seade "
"<quote>lülitub sisse</quote>, mida näitab käivituv <interface>tulemuste "
"arvestaja</interface>. Nüüd saad <action>valida raskusastme</action>:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:142
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Select difficulty level</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Raskusastme valimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:148
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Select difficulty level</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Raskusastme valimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid "There are 3 levels in &blinken;:"
msgstr "&blinken; pakub kolme raskusastet:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level 1 is the easiest level, as it provides the longest time break between "
"each sequence playback."
msgstr "1. tase on lihtsaim, jättes suurima vahe iga jada esitamise vahele."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level 2 is the intermediate level. It is identical to the previous level, "
"but has a smaller time break between each sequence playback."
msgstr ""
"2. tase on keskmise raskusastmega. Üldiselt sarnaneb see esimesele tasemele, "
"kuid jadade esitamise intervall on kiirem."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:169
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Level ? is the most difficult level of &blinken;. It takes the timings from "
"Level 2, but each sequence is totally random, rather than following on from "
"the previous sequence, as in the standard game type."
msgstr ""
"Tase ? on &blinken;i raskeim tase. Intervall on küll sama teise tasemega, "
"kuid jadad on täiesti juhuslikud, mitte kindlas järjekorras, nagu standardse "
"mängu korral."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid "Entering a New Highscore"
msgstr "Uue rekordi sisestamine"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are lucky enough to get a highscore, it will be entered into the "
"<guilabel>Highscores</guilabel> table. A dialog will ask for a name to "
"associate with your score in the table:"
msgstr ""
"Kui sul õnnestub rekord püstitada, lisatakse see <guilabel>rekordite tabel</"
"guilabel>isse. Ühtlasi ilmub dialoog, mis soovib teada nime, mida uue "
"rekordiga seostada:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Highscore nickname prompt dialog</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Rekordiomaniku nime küsimine</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:191
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Highscore nickname prompt dialog</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Rekordiomaniku nime küsimine</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Only 5 scores are kept for each level, so try not to be disappointed if you "
"don't make it!"
msgstr ""
"Iga taseme kohta säilitatakse ainult viis parimat tulemust, nii et ära "
"kurvasta, kui sa kohe rekordit ei püstita!"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Playing Tips"
msgstr "Nõuanded"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&blinken; is the ultimate memory game, though you need not possess the "
"ultimate memory to be successful. These tips will help you in your pursuit "
"of the best score:"
msgstr ""
"&blinken; on täiuslik meelespidamismäng, kuigi edu saavutamiseks pole just "
"vajalik täiuslik meelespidamine. Järgmised nõuanded aitavad sul loodetavasti "
"häid tulemusi saavutada ja rekordeid püstitada:"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have PC speakers, turn them on with the sound at a good level so that "
"you can hear the tones alongside seeing the flashing lights."
msgstr ""
"Kui sinu arvutil on kõlarid, lülita need sisse ja määra helitugevus päris "
"korralikuks, et võiksid lisaks valgusmängule ka helisid kuulda."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Experiment with both the mouse and <link linkend=\"accessibility\">keyboard</"
"link> interaction methods, to see which one suites your memory best."
msgstr ""
"Proovi tegutsemist nii hiirega kui <link linkend=\"accessibility"
"\">klaviatuurilt</link>, et selgitada, milline neist annab sinu puhul "
"paremaid tulemusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try remembering the sequence as a list of colors."
msgstr "Püüa jada meelde jätta värvide reana."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:227
#, no-c-format
msgid "Try remembering the sequence as positions on the screen."
msgstr "Püüa jada meelde jätta asukohtade järgi aknas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessibility Options"
msgstr "Hõlbustusvõimalused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To allow &blinken; to be more easily enjoyed by certain users, there are "
"several accessibility options built into &blinken;."
msgstr ""
"Et &blinken;it võiksid nautida võimalikult paljud inimesed, pakub &blinken; "
"mitmesuguseid hõlbustusvõimalusi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To view and modify the accessibility options of &blinken;, press the &Ctrl; "
"key (whilst a game is not in progress):"
msgstr ""
"&blinken;i hõlbustusvõimaluste vaatamiseks ja muutmiseks vajuta klahvi "
"&Ctrl; (ajal, mis mäng parajasti ei käi)."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:248
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>&blinken; access keys</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&blinken;i liikumisklahvid</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:254
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>&blinken; access keys</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&blinken;i liikumisklahvid</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid "To return to the game screen, press the &Ctrl; key again."
msgstr "Ekraanile naasmiseks vajuta uuesti klahvi &Ctrl;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:263
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alongside use of the mouse, &blinken; also allows the user to operate the "
"game using the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Lisaks hiirele lubab &blinken; kasutajal tegutseda ka ainult klaviatuuri "
"kasutades."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:267
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The keys are <keycap>1</keycap>, <keycap>2</keycap>, <keycap>3</keycap>, "
"<keycap>4</keycap> by default."
msgstr ""
"Klahvid on vaikimisi <keycap>1</keycap>, <keycap>2</keycap>, <keycap>3</"
"keycap> ja <keycap>4</keycap>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the mapping of any button, click it using the mouse. It will then "
"be highlighted, waiting for input. Press the desired key on the keyboard to "
"change the currently assigned key."
msgstr ""
"Suvalise nupu klahviseose muutmiseks klõpsa sellele hiirega. Nupp tõstetakse "
"esile ja oodatakse sinu järgmist sammu. Klahviseose muutmiseks vajuta nüüd "
"lihtsalt klaviatuuril sobivat klahvi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:275
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"There are other options available in the middle of the window: "
"<interface>Sounds</interface> and <interface>Font</interface>."
msgstr ""
"Akna keskel on ootel veel mõned võimalused: <interface>helid</interface> ja "
"<interface>font</interface>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:281
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By unchecking the <interface>Sounds</interface> checkbox, the &blinken; "
"sound effects will be suppressed."
msgstr ""
"Eemaldades märke kastist <interface>helid</interface>, ei too &blinken; enam "
"mingeid helisid kuuldavale."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:286
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By unchecking the <interface>Font</interface> checkbox, a standard font will "
"be used for status text instead of the default handwriting font."
msgstr ""
"Eemaldades märke kastist <interface>font</interface>, kasutatakse "
"olekuteksti näitamiseks standardset fonti, mitte rakenduses muidu "
"pruugitavat käekirja moodi fonti."

